WITH TMP_CEL_CONTRACT AS (
    SELECT 
        * ,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY "InitialUniqueName" 
            ORDER BY 
                CAST("VersionNumber" AS integer) DESC
        ) AS RN
    FROM "Contract"
    WHERE 1=1
        AND "Contract"."Active" = 'true'
)
